# API contract is the source of truth
- `docs/openapi.yaml` defines all 9 endpoints, request/response shapes, and status codes.
- Every endpoint returns the documented status codes, especially 409 (duplicate / checkout conflict) and 422 (invalid transition).
- Validate auth: only `@sparkrobotic.com` emails get a session.
- Do not begin parallel/worktree work until this contract is frozen for the milestone.
